    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People or corporate bodies who perform work or provide supplies, often on a large scale, according to a legally binding contractual agreement at a certain price or rate. For example, in the building and related trades, contractors undertake construction work according to the terms of a contract.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
